column1: Total land, by region and States, United States, 1945-2012 1/
1/ Land area established by the Bureau of the Census in conjunction with various Censuses of Population.
Includes all land area and water, such as marshland, swamps, and river floodplains; streams, estuaries,
and canals less than one-eighth mile wide; and lakes, reservoirs, and ponds less than 40 acres in area.
Footnotes to other files may be applicable.
2/ Distributions may not add to totals due to rounding.
